CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776359147
OL,3,CUK economy grew faster than expected
OL,4,Cin February
OL,6,FThe UK economy grew at its fastest
OL,7,Fpace in more than a year in February,
OL,8,Fmarking a better-than-expected start
OL,9,Fto 2026, official figures have shown.
OL,11,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,12,F(ONS) said gross domestic product
OL,13,F(GDP) grew by 0.5% month-on-month in
OL,14,FFebruary following upwardly revised
OL,15,Fgrowth of 0.1% in January.
OL,17,FMost economists had forecast GDP to
OL,18,Frise by just 0.1% in February, while
OL,19,Fthe ONS had previously estimated no
OL,20,Fgrowth in January.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
