CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776359147
OL,3,CUK economy grew faster than expected
OL,4,Cin February
OL,6,FBut the figures come amid forecasts
OL,7,Fthat Britain's output will be hardest
OL,8,Fhit this year by the fallout from the
OL,9,FIran war and soaring energy costs.
OL,11,FA stark economic outlook report from
OL,12,Fthe International Monetary Fund (IMF)
OL,13,Fearlier this week showed the UK facing
OL,14,Fthe biggest downgrade to growth among
OL,15,Fthe G7 group of countries, with 0.8%
OL,16,Fforecast for 2026, down sharply from
OL,17,Fthe 1.3% predicted in January.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
