OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776359147
OL,3,CUK economy grew faster than expected
OL,4,Cin February
OL,6,FChief Secretary to the Treasury James
OL,7,FMurray said: "Growth only happens when
OL,8,Fthe economy is on solid ground. That's
OL,9,Fwhy in a changing world our plan to
OL,10,Frestore stability, boost investment
OL,11,Fand deliver reform is the right one to
OL,12,Fbuild a more stronger more resilient
OL,13,FBritain.
OL,26,@oD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
