CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776359147
OL,3,CUK economy grew faster than expected
OL,4,Cin February
OL,6,F"At the IMF meetings in Washington,
OL,7,Fthe Chancellor has set out how we will
OL,8,Fgo further and faster to boost
OL,9,FBritain's competitiveness and build a
OL,10,Fstronger, more resilient economy,
OL,11,Fkeeping costs down for families and
OL,12,Fbusinesses and taking back control of
OL,13,Four energy costs as today we cut bills
OL,14,Fby up to 25% for 10,000 British
OL,15,Fbusinesses."
OL,17,FThe ONS said in the three months to
OL,18,FFebruary, GDP rose by 0.5% following
OL,19,Fgrowth of 0.3% in the three months to
OL,20,FJanuary, revised up from the previous
OL,21,Festimation of 0.2%.
