OL,3,CUK economy grew faster than expected
OL,4,Cin February
OL,6,FHowever, the ONS revised its figure
OL,7,Ffor the three months to December 2025
OL,8,Fdown to zero growth.
OL,10,FGrant Fitzner, chief economist at the
OL,11,FONS, said growth in February was "led
OL,12,Fby broad-based increases across
OL,13,Fservices".
