OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776359147
OL,3,CUK economy grew faster than expected
OL,4,Cin February
OL,6,FServices output grew by 0.5% month-on-
OL,7,Fmonth in February, while manufacturing
OL,8,Factivity contracted by 0.1% and
OL,9,Fconstruction saw a 1% rebound.
OL,11,FThe services growth was driven by
OL,12,Fwholesaling, market research,
OL,13,Fhospitality and publishing, which all
OL,14,Fperformed well in the three months to
OL,15,FFebruary.
OL,17,FMr Fitzner also said car production
OL,18,Frecovered from the effects of last
OL,19,Fyear's cyber incident, which knocked a
OL,20,Flarge amount of Jaguar Land Rover's
OL,21,Finfrastructure offline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
