OL,3,CUK economy grew faster than expected
OL,4,Cin February
OL,6,FShadow chancellor Sir Mel Stride said:
OL,7,F"Any economic growth is welcome, but
OL,8,Fthe IMF were clear this week that
OL,9,Funder Labour our economy is totally
OL,10,Funprepared for the recent energy
OL,11,Fshock."
